{
  "stem": "3835.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But when we went to sleep the 18th of September, 1939, in the middle of the night, about 3, 4 o'clock in the morning, we heard tanks are coming.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Tanks are coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Instead, we go to Russia, the Russian army crossed the Polish border and came to Poland through their border.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We thought that they are going to help the Polish army to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there were a pact made between Hitler and Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They take the western half of Poland and Russia take the eastern half of Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this was the story.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And suddenly, overnight, we are Russians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We are no more Poles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We are Russians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Naturally, I-- we were on the border town, which is called Ostrog nad Horyniem.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the border.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After being there a few days, what do we do in this small town?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We went to the big town, like, I would say, 20 or 25 miles west, Rovno.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was already the big eastern Polish town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we started there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The money, the $100, wasn't going-- like, I lived for $1 a day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They opened a kitchen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were called in Russian [RUSSIAN], displaced persons, which we didn't have homes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were without homes, [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But since the Jews in Rovno, very fine-- very fine Jews, with big hearts, everybody opened the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody-- Because they were in the same bowl as we where.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Naturally, they saw in the meantime-- they were Russian, but they didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Russians, in the beginning the army came in, the Russian army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had nothing to do with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the first thing, I took-- I bought a Russian book, how to read  and how to write Russian.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
